title: A Little Princess (1995)
description:
This is a movie everyone ought to have. Whenever the world is falling down around you ears and everything is all wrong, that is the time to bring out this video and relax. It's remarkable how it changes your whole attitude.
My wife and I have noticed that both this one and Hans Christen Andersen have 
have that magical ability to make you happy.

I hope you agree.
